title: Status Saver for WhatsApp
description:
Using status saver for WhatsApp you can download any status videos and images right to your gallery!

In this way, you can enjoy downloaded status photos and videos anytime, anywhere. Status downloader also supports WhatsApp Business. How to Use? 1: Open whatsapp and check the desired statuses 2: Open status saver, click on any image or video 3: Click the download button OR 1: Open whatsapp and check the desired statuses 2: Hold on a status to enable multi-selection 3: Click on the save icon from the toolbar menu The status image or video is instantly saved to your gallery! Some of the features: ⭐ Multi save, repost, share ⭐ Easy & fast saving ⭐ Built in image viewer & video player ⭐ Easy to use ⭐ View status of friends without seen ⭐ Images & videos in different tabs ⭐ Supports WhatsApp Business ⭐ Support downloading both video and photo ⭐ Play videos offline with the built-in video player ⭐ View photos offline with the built-in gallery ⭐ Easy to share or repost downloaded videos and photos ⭐ Lightweight This app is not affiliated with WhatsApp
descriptionHTML:
Using status saver for WhatsApp you can download any status videos and images right to your gallery!



In this way, you can enjoy downloaded status photos and videos anytime, anywhere. Status downloader also supports WhatsApp Business.

How to Use?
1: Open whatsapp and check the desired statuses
2: Open status saver, click on any image or video
3: Click the download button

OR

1: Open whatsapp and check the desired statuses
2: Hold on a status to enable multi-selection
3: Click on the save icon from the toolbar menu

The status image or video is instantly saved to your gallery!

Some of the features:
⭐ Multi save, repost, share
⭐ Easy & fast saving
⭐ Built in image viewer & video player
⭐ Easy to use
⭐ View status of friends without seen
⭐ Images & videos in different tabs
⭐ Supports WhatsApp Business
⭐ Support downloading both video and photo
⭐ Play videos offline with the built-in video player
⭐ View photos offline with the built-in gallery
⭐ Easy to share or repost downloaded videos and photos
⭐ Lightweight

This app is not affiliated with WhatsApp
summary: View and save statuses of WhatsApp to your gallery.
summaryHTML: View and save statuses of WhatsApp to your gallery.

title: Subway Surfers
description:
DASH as fast as you can! 
DODGE the oncoming trains! 

Help Jake, Tricky & Fresh escape from the grumpy Inspector and his dog. 

★ Grind trains with your cool crew! 
★ Colorful and vivid HD graphics! 
★ Hoverboard Surfing! 
★ Paint powered jetpack! 
★ Lightning fast swipe acrobatics! 
★ Challenge and help your friends! 

Join the most daring chase! 

A Universal App with HD optimized graphics.

By Kiloo and Sybo.
